---
title: Lobster Ravioli in a Lemony Cream Sauce with Blistered Tomatoes & Spinach Salad
description: Ravioli is an Italian classic, and here it's enhanced with a sweet, luxe lobster filling and a silky lemon-garlic cream sauce. To balance out the richness, juicy grape tomatoes are charred in a pan for a hit of acidity, and bacon-studded, citrus-tossed spinach salad lends some freshness. Finally, the ravioli is topped with wilted spinach, Parmesan, and toasted panko for a delightful crunch. Trust us when we say this restaurant-worthy dish is the whole package.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/lobster-ravioli-in-a-lemon-garlic-cream-sauce-88c90ece.jpg
